{"tid":1722691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[中大人入] 學生會比人蝦緊","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T04:09:40.000Z","uid":194558,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"53ce9a0c2800c6ff9ede9498e58273e1864439c2","tid":1722691,"uid":194558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Br1Rirg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBr1Rirg.png&h=d48b3590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇CU secret<br />\n<br />\n宜家個問題係 有一班非中大人嘅前線態度好差又唔肯聽中大學生嘅意見, 甚至以武力兇鳩學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話要裝修又話要燒SU/ 宿 <br />\n<br />\n到底當外界同傳媒係到不停講話支援學生嘅時候, 呢班所謂支援學生嘅前線有冇尊重過我校學生? 係一個學校環境入面, 學生是否應有多d 主導權? <br />\n<br />\n若然你要入中大態度咁惡劣地做土皇帝去 &ldquo;保護&rdquo; 我地咁不如你走啦, 我地自己搞掂。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n我認為中大情況可以有兩個方案: </span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 我地中大人走曬, 反正都完左sem, 冇曬學生, 等佢地守空城。 變左空城就算狗攻左入黎都唔會有發現同損傷。<br />\n2. 集合中大人，透過中大學生會集合民意轉達比前線, 佢地唔聽我地就以人多咁圍到佢地走為止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n中大人點睇?"},{"pid":"82679037b1da05f4040a7e24d244966e7a398e54","tid":1722691,"uid":194558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:21:15.000Z","msg":"推比中大人睇"},{"pid":"8c96d2fece0e82d67f9b033c36131ce160344569","tid":1722691,"uid":194558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:21:31.000Z","msg":"求下大家"},{"pid":"2790949fdd7ebf6c81476d853e7b8cd63323d433","tid":1722691,"uid":194558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"救救中大"},{"pid":"33bde9bd43008f3a19e2181f5584d068b5b4a779","tid":1722691,"uid":194558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:22:00.000Z","msg":"唔好比外人蝦學生"},{"pid":"dc39043e30d9f1eb403b1a8c0203868bc121d6cb","tid":1722691,"uid":283508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cite